<h1 style="font-size:200%; text-align:center;">Services</h1>
<p>Modify Interiors is an Astana based boutique design studio that offers high-end residential interior design/renovation services. Design services are priced on a flat fee scale based on the scope of work. In addition, all trade discounts are passed on to the client with no mark-up.</p>
<hr>
<p>There are essentially three stages to the process:</p>

<p>IMAGINE•</p>
<p>initial consultation to discuss and evaluate the overall vision for your space</p>
<hr>
<p>PLAN•</p>
<p>prepare a detailed proposal based on our initial consultation</p>
<hr>
<p>CREATE•</p>
<p>execute the plan to create the space you imagined</p>

